
PROGRAMMING PRINCIPLES : 30 days

Topics
- INTRO (terminologies)
	. Computer Program
	. Programming
	. Programming Language
	. Source Code(Program)
	. Object Code
	. Syntax
	. Semantics

- LANGUAGE TRANSLATORS 
	(1)Assembler.
	(2)Interpreter.
	(3)Compiler.

	+ Linker, Loader

- LEVELS OF PROGRAMMING LANGUAGES
	(1)Low-level languages.
	(2)High-level languages.

	+ programming language Generations
		~ 1st - 5th Gen

- PROGRAM DEVELOPMENT CYCLE
	. Problem Recognition 
	. Problem Definition
	. Program Design
	. Program Coding
	. Program Testing and Debugging
 	. Program Implementation and Maintenance
	. Program Documentation

- DEVELOPING OF ALGORITHMS
	. algorithm terminologies
	. Qualities of a good Algorithm
	. Program Design Tools
		 Pseudocodes and Flowcharts.

- PROGRAM CONTROL STRUCTURES
	Control structures
	Types of Control structures 
	 sequential 
		statement 1, statement 2 etc.
	 Selection (Decision)
		. if then ( one option ) 
		. if else then ( two options ) 
		. if elseif else (more than two )
		. Case of (switch case) 
		. nested if blocks

	 iteration (Looping/Repetition)
		. for loop
		. while loop
		. do while / repeat ... until loop
		. nested loops

- ADDITIONAL TOPICS 
	- Operating system basics 
		windows or linux
	- Number systems 
		binary , octal ,
		decimal and hexadecimal

- SELECTING YOUR FIRST LANGUAGE
	~ things to consider:
		age 
		computer skills and math
		programming experience 
			. absolute beginner
			. second language
	~ recommended: c, java, c#, python, 
		         ~ javascript, c++
	
